leaders in tower and pole  design and manufacturing telescoping masts available in    and  heights all rohn  telescoping masts are pregalvanized and come assembled with hardware erecting the telescoping mast is made by simply connecting guys and brackets to the attached unique heavy duty rolled edge guy rings and clamps extend the sections insert the locking cotter pins rotating the tubes to a locked position and tightening the clamps the unique rohn telescoping mast design features interior tube flanging combined with a double crimped exterior tube to produce a stronger and more stable joint than most common masts this exclusive design also prevents the sections from accidentally pulling apart and allows disassembly by pulling each section out through the lower end each section extends deeper in to the lower tubes than most other telescoping mast designs adding still further to the stability of the structure h series this heavy duty series of telescoping masts uses   gauge galvanized tubing for top section all other sections are  gauge product information telescoping masts connect with the right person to better serve the needs of our customers we have separated our sales team by customer segment telecommunications sales international sales transportation sales utility sales  wind energy sales light duty tower series sales rohn distributors     if you have any questions comments or suggestions regarding any of our products we are just a phone call away    rohn products llc  selfsupporting towers vertical structures built to last       the world leaders in tower and pole  design and manufacturing self supporting towers backed by one of the largest manufacturing facilities of communication towers in the world rohn selfsupporting towers are produced with unmatched attention to detail our towers are hotdip galvanized after fabrication to assure years of corrosionfree use in this process rohn tower manufacturing company immerses each section of the selfsupporting tower 